pageContent: Introduction: To investigate the efficacy, safety and postoperative outcomes of using tadalafil and low-intensity extracorporeal shock wave therapy (Li-ESWT) on penile rehabilitation and preventing urinary incontinence after radical prostatectomy.

metaData.source:
Factors influencing self-esteem after radical prostatectomy in older adult patients
